WEBVTT


00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:07.360
New laws for foreign health and care workers

00:00:07.360 --> 00:00:11.060
to come into effect from March 11th, 2024.

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:16.200
Migrating to the UK for health and care workers

00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:17.440
is becoming tough

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:19.640
as new rules restrict them from bringing

00:00:19.640 --> 00:00:21.140
independence to the UK

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:23.400
watch this video till the end

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:25.860
to know the details of this new regulation.

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.400
Downing Street says that a crackdown on foreign worker

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:33.060
visas is under review.

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:36.260
As a result of this statement,

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:38.760
anxiety spreads that the Home Office

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:40.880
has authorized hundreds of new care

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:42.860
providers to sponsor foreign workers.

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:47.120
Moreover, the government has imposed these laws

00:00:47.120 --> 00:00:50.020
to drop the record levels of immigration to Britain.
